sentences: Kristinia Jamie DeBarge (; born March 8, 1990) is an American singer, songwriter, dancer and actress.
DeBarge first appeared on national television in 2003 as a contestant on the American Idol spin-off, American Juniors.
In 2009, DeBarge signed a contract with the Island Records department Sodapop, releasing her debut album, Exposed, in July of the same year.
Born in 1990, DeBarge is the daughter of James DeBarge.
